<h1>ICME 2003</h1>
<p>Thank you all for making ICME 2003 a wonderful success! More than 760 papers submitted to ICME 2003
from 52 countries; 440 were accepted for presentation in either oral or poster sessions. Additionally, 150 papers accepted for
<a href="http://www.icassp2003.com" target="_blank">ICASSP 2003</a> were presented. Over 600 attended ICME 2003.</p>

<p>View some of the memorable moments in pictures in the <a href="ImageGallery/">photo gallery</a>.</p>
