<p>Dear ICME 2003 attendees,</p>

<p>On behalf of the Organizing committee, let me welcome you all to the fourth International Conference on 
Multimedia and Expo (ICME 2003). The first three ICME conferences were held in New York, Tokyo, and Lausanne. 
